select DISTINCT i.ssn from invopt_alloc ia left join individual i on i.id = ia.ind_id where ga_id in (select distinct acv1.ga_id from access_customization_view acv1 inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id= acv1.ga_id and uda.user_logon_id=? and acv1.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv1.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' where not EXISTS(select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv1.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs')) and termdate is null

select distinct ga.id ga_id from group_account ga inner join access_customization_view acv on acv.ga_id=ga.id inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id = acv.ga_id where ga.prod_id in(select id from product where irsrl_code in('NQDC', '457B', 'NQSP')) and ga.plan_type in('DAILYVAL', 'BAL FWD' ,'DLYVALME') and acv.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' and uda.user_logon_id=? and not EXISTS (select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs')

select distinct ga.id ga_id from group_account ga inner join access_customization_view acv on acv.ga_id=ga.id inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id = acv.ga_id where ga.plan_type in('DEF BEN', 'DEFBENME') and acv.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' and uda.user_logon_id=? and not EXISTS (select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs')

select e.union_ind,e.insider_ind, e.super_officer_ind,e.full_part_time_employee,e.job_descr, e.employment_type, e.er_classification_code, e.er_classification_chg_dpdate,i.ssn,i.id from employment e inner join individual i on i.id=e.ind_id where ind_id in(select ind_id from part_agrmt where ga_id in (select distinct acv1.ga_id from access_customization_view acv1 inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id= acv1.ga_id and uda.user_logon_id=? and acv1.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv1.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' where not EXISTS(select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv1.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs'))) and e.er_classification_chg_dpdate is not null

select iact.effdate Record_count from inv_acct ia, invopt_acty iact where iact.fat_code in ('CMC','EPA','FAF','SRC','TPA','TPC','TXF') and iact.suppress_ind = 'N' and iact.effdate <= SYSDATE and iact.effdate >= add_months(sysdate,-3) and ia.id = iact.iva_id and ia.ind_id in (select id from individual where ssn=?) and ia.ga_id in (select distinct acv1.ga_id from access_customization_view acv1 inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id= acv1.ga_id and uda.user_logon_id=? and acv1.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv1.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' where not EXISTS(select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv1.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs'))

select distinct i.ssn from inv_acct ia, invopt_acty iact, individual i where iact.effdate NOT Between SYSDATE and add_months(sysdate,-3) and iact.fat_code in ('CMC','EPA','FAF','SRC','TPA','TPC','TXF') and iact.suppress_ind = 'N' and i.id= ia.ind_id and ia.id = iact.iva_id and ia.ga_id in (select distinct acv1.ga_id from access_customization_view acv1 inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id= acv1.ga_id and uda.user_logon_id=? and acv1.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv1.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' where not EXISTS(select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv1.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs')) and rownum <100

select ssn from individual where id in( select pa.ind_id from part_agrmt pa, loan_acct la where pa.ind_id = la.ind_id and la.status_code in ( 'A','P') and pa.status_code in ( 'A','P') and pa.ga_id in (select distinct acv1.ga_id from access_customization_view acv1 inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id= acv1.ga_id and uda.user_logon_id=? and acv1.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv1.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' where not EXISTS(select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv1.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs')) and pa.ind_id = la.ind_id group by pa.ind_id having count(pa.ind_id) > 5) order by ssn desc

select to_char(effdate,'MM/DD/YYYY') effdate, loan_amt, status_code, repay_amt, inlnag_seqnbr from loan_acct where ind_id in (select id from individual where ssn=?) and status_code in ('P','A') order by to_date(effdate,'mm/dd/yyyy') desc

select to_char(effdate,'MM/dd/yyyy') effdate, to_char(first_due_date,'MM/dd/yyyy') first_due_date, to_char(maturity_date,'MM/dd/yyyy') maturity_date, fixed_int_rate, loan_term, orig_loan_amt, status_code,default_ind from loan_acct where ind_id in (select id from individual where ssn=?) and inlnag_seqnbr=?
select due_date from loan_assess where ind_id in(select id from individual where ssn=?)and status_code in ('UNPAID','PARTIAL') and inlnag_seqnbr=? order by due_date asc

SELECT GDM.SDMT_CODE , AG.GDMT_SEQNBR , GDM.DESCR , to_char(SUM(IR.AMOUNT),'999999999999999.00') amount from IND_REMIT IR, AG_REMIT AG , REMIT_NOTICE RN , GRP_DEF_MNTY GDM where RN.ID = AG.RMNC_ID and IR.RMNC_ID = AG.RMNC_ID AND GDM.GA_ID = RN.GA_ID AND GDM.SDMT_CODE = AG.SDMT_CODE AND GDM.SEQNBR = AG.GDMT_SEQNBR and IR.AGRM_SEQNBR = AG.SEQNBR AND IR.PROCESS_STATUS_CODE = 'D' AND AG.SDDETY_CODE = 'REG' AND nvl(AG.PAYROLL_DATE,RN.CASH_EFFDATE) BETWEEN trunc(sysdate,'YEAR') and sysdate AND RN.CASH_EFFDATE <= trunc(sysdate) AND RN.CSRS_CODE = 'PAYROLL' and RN.GA_ID = ? and IR.IND_ID in(select id from individual where ssn=?) GROUP BY GDM.SDMT_CODE , AG.GDMT_SEQNBR , GDM.DESCR

select distinct i.ssn from inv_acct ia, invopt_acty iva,individual i where i.id =ia.ind_id and ia.id=iva.iva_id and ia.effdate= iva.effdate and ia.ga_id in (select distinct acv1.ga_id from access_customization_view acv1 inner join user_data_access uda on uda.ga_id= acv1.ga_id and uda.user_logon_id=? and acv1.accu_code='PlanEmpower' and acv1.access_type_code='PSC_WEB' where not EXISTS(select * from access_customization_view acv2 where acv1.ga_id= acv2.ga_id and acv2.accu_code='PscGwrs')) and ia.effdate not between trunc(sysdate,'YEAR') and sysdate and rownum<50
